WEBVTT

00:02.419 --> 00:04.888
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.888 --> 00:06.890
Sam, two nights ago on the boat,

00:06.890 --> 00:09.893
you demonstrated in no uncertain terms

00:09.893 --> 00:11.895
that you and I are inevitable.

00:11.895 --> 00:14.898
You said those words I had
hoped to hear for so long,

00:14.898 --> 00:17.267
"Will you marry me?"

00:17.267 --> 00:20.653
Before thinking, I responded no.

00:20.653 --> 00:22.939
But then I realized all I needed

00:22.939 --> 00:26.443
was some time alone to clear my mind.

00:26.443 --> 00:30.830
Now I have returned to you
with a resounding "yes."

00:30.830 --> 00:32.698
Say, Sam,

00:32.698 --> 00:35.668
I don't like it any more than you do,

00:35.668 --> 00:38.038
but I've decided to accept it.

00:38.038 --> 00:39.956
Therefore, I am going to work here

00:39.956 --> 00:41.458
so that when you finally accept it,

00:41.458 --> 00:42.959
as we both know you will,

00:42.959 --> 00:46.463
we can move forward to build
and nurture our relationship.

00:46.463 --> 00:48.348
Excuse me. I have customers to wait on.

00:48.348 --> 00:49.682
No, you...!

00:49.682 --> 00:52.102
Listen, listen, I, I
don't want you here.

00:52.102 --> 00:53.603
I don't want you in the building.

00:53.603 --> 00:55.605
I don't want you on this planet.

00:55.605 --> 00:56.606
He's crazy about me.

00:56.606 --> 00:58.108
No, I'm not crazy about her.

00:58.108 --> 01:00.110
You make me sick to my stomach.

01:00.110 --> 01:01.561
That's how I am about her.

01:01.561 --> 01:03.530
We have kind of a little thing going.

01:05.031 --> 01:07.033
Now, what would you like?

01:07.033 --> 01:09.035
I'm sorry. This isn't my table.

01:10.537 --> 01:11.538
Miss Chambers?

01:13.039 --> 01:14.541
You know I'm your friend

01:14.541 --> 01:16.543
and friends should stick together,

01:16.543 --> 01:19.546
so I'm really happy you're back.

01:19.546 --> 01:21.047
Oh, Woody, thanks.

01:23.049 --> 01:25.802
Well, kind of happy,
'cause Sam's my friend, too.

01:25.802 --> 01:27.637
So I can't be too happy

01:27.637 --> 01:32.142
or else he'll can me, which
will make me really sad.

01:32.142 --> 01:36.146
And I know you, as my friend,
wouldn't be happy about that.

01:36.146 --> 01:40.150
So, whatever you do, don't
tell Sam what I just told you.

01:40.150 --> 01:43.069
What did you just tell me?

01:43.069 --> 01:44.938
Perfect.

01:47.323 --> 01:51.194
(piano plays)

01:51.194 --> 01:53.663
? Making your way in the world today ?

01:53.663 --> 01:56.666
? Takes everything you've got ?

01:56.666 --> 01:59.669
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

01:59.669 --> 02:02.672
? Sure would help a lot ?

02:02.672 --> 02:07.927
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

02:07.927 --> 02:10.713
? Sometimes you want to go ?

02:10.713 --> 02:15.718
? Where everybody knows your name ?

02:15.718 --> 02:20.723
? And they're always glad you came ?

02:20.723 --> 02:22.725
? You want to be where you can see ?

02:22.725 --> 02:25.728
? Our troubles are all the same ?

02:25.728 --> 02:30.733
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

02:30.733 --> 02:33.736
? You want to go where people know ?

02:33.736 --> 02:35.738
? People are all the same ?

02:36.239 --> 02:40.743
? You want to go where
everybody knows your name. ?

