14:39.128 --> 14:40.996
Like you're getting all
dolled up for some hot action.

14:42.882 --> 14:44.884
What does that sound like?

14:44.884 --> 14:45.885
Uh, eh, I don't know.

14:45.885 --> 14:47.386
Whatever you and Harvey do...

14:47.386 --> 14:48.387
Never mind. Never mind.

14:48.387 --> 14:49.388
Just, uh...

14:49.388 --> 14:50.890
Here you go. $50.

14:52.892 --> 14:54.393
(knocking)

14:57.897 --> 14:59.899
Hi, Sam. Hey.

14:59.899 --> 15:01.150
Where's Vicki?

15:01.150 --> 15:02.985
She's, uh, still in the bathroom.

15:03.485 --> 15:06.488
Well, I'll just wait. Huh?

15:07.940 --> 15:09.441
No, uh...

15:09.441 --> 15:11.443
You know, um...

15:11.443 --> 15:12.945
this could take a little while here.

15:12.945 --> 15:13.946
Why don't you, uh,

15:14.446 --> 15:18.334
why don't you just yell your
apologies through the door here?

15:18.334 --> 15:19.201
Oh, that's silly.

15:19.201 --> 15:20.703
I'll be here all weekend.

15:20.703 --> 15:21.704
I can certainly wait.

15:21.704 --> 15:24.873
(woman laughing)

15:27.459 --> 15:29.261
(laughing)

15:29.261 --> 15:31.931
She sure is busy.

15:33.182 --> 15:34.183
Is that enough

15:34.183 --> 15:37.186
or should we snap some towels?

15:44.393 --> 15:46.695
It's the, uh, bathroom inspector.

15:46.695 --> 15:47.696
It's a new thing.

15:49.615 --> 15:50.616
Sam...

15:50.616 --> 15:52.484
let's call an end to
this nonsense right now.

15:52.484 --> 15:54.486
I don't care how rough you were on her;

15:54.486 --> 15:58.490
that is not Vicki.

15:58.490 --> 16:00.492
See, I know Vicki left.

16:00.492 --> 16:03.996
I've known all along.

16:03.996 --> 16:06.999
And you let me go through
this whole stupid act?

16:06.999 --> 16:10.502
Well, I wanted to
see how far you'd go--

16:10.502 --> 16:12.755
ordering two sets of meals,

16:12.755 --> 16:14.556
leaving empty bottles of Vitamin E

16:14.556 --> 16:17.559
outside your door...

16:17.559 --> 16:18.927
Yeah, well, what about you?

16:18.927 --> 16:21.313
You know, coming all the
way up here to spy on me?

16:21.313 --> 16:24.183
Oh, don't be ridiculous.

16:24.183 --> 16:25.351
Yeah?

16:27.903 --> 16:29.822
What's the use?

16:29.822 --> 16:32.191
We both look like imbeciles.

16:32.191 --> 16:34.526
All we do is find new ways

16:34.526 --> 16:38.530
to humiliate each other.

16:38.530 --> 16:41.417
I humiliate you by saying "no"

16:41.417 --> 16:44.370
to your sweet proposal.

16:44.370 --> 16:47.756
You humiliate me by
rejecting my retraction.

16:47.756 --> 16:49.675
You carry off this ridiculous charade.

16:49.675 --> 16:51.593
I spy on you in hotel rooms.

16:51.593 --> 16:54.096
It's become sick and degrading.

16:54.096 --> 16:55.097
And, quite frankly,

16:55.097 --> 16:57.466
I'm embarrassed to be a
part of it, Sam. Yeah, well,

16:57.466 --> 16:59.301
I'm not too thrilled
you're part of it either.

17:01.186 --> 17:03.689
Here you go, pal.

17:03.689 --> 17:04.690
Oh...

17:08.694 --> 17:10.695
Oh, yeah, yeah.

17:10.695 --> 17:13.198
I guess this all looks
pretty weird, doesn't it?

17:13.198 --> 17:15.200
Oh, nothing I haven't seen before.

17:19.204 --> 17:21.707
I believe you owe us $50.

17:21.707 --> 17:24.209
Now there's a new one.

17:28.714 --> 17:30.582
Boy, Carla, you know, I never thought

17:30.582 --> 17:33.585
you'd be able to unload all
those kittens in one night.

17:33.585 --> 17:35.087
Yeah, it was just a simple matter

17:35.087 --> 17:36.588
of marketing technique, you know.

17:36.588 --> 17:38.090
Giving away a beer with each kitten

17:38.090 --> 17:39.475
really did the trick.

17:45.314 --> 17:46.765
Come on.

17:46.765 --> 17:47.766
Here, Toots,

17:47.766 --> 17:51.687
time for your first cab ride.

17:51.687 --> 17:53.689
You know you guys are
really gonna love Vera.

17:53.689 --> 17:56.191
She has legs just
like a scratching post.

18:12.841 --> 18:14.593
Oh, good evening.

18:14.593 --> 18:16.095
Good evening.

18:28.107 --> 18:30.859
Oh, it's you.

18:32.728 --> 18:34.229
Small world.

18:34.229 --> 18:35.614
Mm...

18:35.614 --> 18:38.734
I thought I was eating late
enough to avoid seeing you.

18:38.734 --> 18:40.319
Me, too.

18:40.319 --> 18:42.204
The only reason why I
waited so long to eat.

18:42.204 --> 18:44.656
Oh, I thought perhaps it was because

18:44.656 --> 18:46.158
you've been eating for two.

18:51.296 --> 18:53.715
(sighs)

18:56.418 --> 18:57.920
I'm kind of glad you're here.

18:57.920 --> 18:59.671
I've been sitting here
driving myself crazy.

18:59.671 --> 19:01.223
When we used to come here,

19:01.223 --> 19:04.393
wasn't there a lobster
trap out in the lobby?

19:04.393 --> 19:06.812
Oh, yeah.

19:06.812 --> 19:08.814
Yeah, I guess the
lobsters finally wised up

19:08.814 --> 19:10.682
and starting coming through the kitchen.

19:10.682 --> 19:12.734
(laughs)

19:19.525 --> 19:22.027
By the way, I suppose
I owe you an apology

19:22.027 --> 19:23.529
for being here this weekend.

19:23.529 --> 19:25.948
In retrospect, I guess...

19:25.948 --> 19:28.867
it was probably a mistake.

19:28.867 --> 19:30.669
Probably?

19:32.421 --> 19:34.923
I'd say "definitely"
if you were to admit

19:34.923 --> 19:38.927
that it was a mistake to
flaunt your date in front of me.

19:40.379 --> 19:41.880
Apology accepted.

19:45.434 --> 19:47.936
Boy, you know the one thing
I really hate is to eat alone.

19:47.936 --> 19:49.805
I always feel like
someone's looking at me.

19:49.805 --> 19:51.974
I'm the only one here.

19:51.974 --> 19:53.775
Well, you're looking at me.

19:58.897 --> 20:02.201
Then you can either join me or
I can eat with my eyes closed.

20:02.201 --> 20:05.988
Well, I hate to have
you butter your knuckles.

20:07.239 --> 20:08.740
Good.

20:12.160 --> 20:14.162
Sam, you know what I remember most

20:14.162 --> 20:16.164
about being here before?

20:16.164 --> 20:17.165
Oh, sure, sure.

20:17.165 --> 20:20.669
Yeah, I think the salt
air gives me extra stamina.

20:25.090 --> 20:27.893
Actually, I was thinking
of the Clams Oregano,

20:27.893 --> 20:30.646
but now that you mention
it, I did enjoy the...

20:30.646 --> 20:33.315
salt air.

20:39.905 --> 20:44.076
Sam, what I said before
about our relationship,

20:44.076 --> 20:45.661
I'm...

20:45.661 --> 20:46.945
I'm sorry I said it.

20:46.945 --> 20:49.331
I was upset.

20:49.331 --> 20:52.117
It may not be ideal, but...

20:52.117 --> 20:55.537
it hasn't been without its moments.

20:58.040 --> 20:59.041
Speaking of moments,

20:59.041 --> 21:02.294
this, uh, is beginning
to feel like one here.

21:05.297 --> 21:07.683
Yes, I think I've decided what I want,

21:07.683 --> 21:09.935
and it's not on the menu.

21:09.935 --> 21:12.271
Oh, you want to skip the main course

21:12.271 --> 21:15.140
