21:17.109 --> 21:19.611
I see you haven't lost
your way with words.

21:26.485 --> 21:27.986
Let's go.

21:27.986 --> 21:28.987
Yes, this is the perfect moment.

21:28.987 --> 21:31.490
But... it is with the understanding,

21:31.490 --> 21:34.376
isn't it, of...

21:34.376 --> 21:37.996
what this step we're
about to take means?

21:37.996 --> 21:39.247
Oh, yeah, yeah, no problem.

21:39.247 --> 21:40.749
If they give us any trouble,

21:40.749 --> 21:41.750
I'll just pay for both rooms.

21:47.222 --> 21:49.091
What it means between us.

21:49.091 --> 21:50.425
Oh, now wait, listen. Listen.

21:50.425 --> 21:52.010
No, it has to mean something, Sam.

21:52.010 --> 21:53.845
I'm only gonna agree to do this if,

21:54.346 --> 21:56.231
if we agree that it
doesn't mean anything.

21:57.566 --> 22:00.435
How can our lovemaking
not mean something?

22:00.435 --> 22:02.571
Well, it's easy. Just concentrate.

22:07.442 --> 22:08.443
I don't want to get caught up

22:08.443 --> 22:10.946
in a war of words with you.

22:10.946 --> 22:15.450
What I'm feeling right
now is very... special,

22:15.951 --> 22:17.953
and I think we should go upstairs

22:17.953 --> 22:19.454
and be with each other

22:19.454 --> 22:21.957
and figure out what it means afterwards.

22:21.957 --> 22:23.208
Let's go.

22:23.208 --> 22:25.544
No.

22:25.544 --> 22:27.045
What?

22:27.546 --> 22:30.048
I-I gotta be clear what I'm doing here.

22:30.048 --> 22:32.434
I mean, my gut's telling me one thing,

22:32.434 --> 22:34.936
but my, my head's telling
me something quite different.

22:36.805 --> 22:38.056
I don't believe what I'm hearing.

22:38.056 --> 22:39.558
(chuckling)

22:39.558 --> 22:41.059
Oh...!

22:41.059 --> 22:42.060
Gotcha.

22:42.060 --> 22:43.562
(laughs)

22:43.562 --> 22:45.814
You were joking? (laughs)

22:45.814 --> 22:47.399
Yeah. How's it feel? I
mean, how do you like it

22:47.399 --> 22:49.618
when you get your motor all revved up

22:49.618 --> 22:52.154
and then someone jerks
the rug out from under you?

22:52.154 --> 22:57.459
Well, mixed metaphors
aside, I don't like it a bit.

22:57.459 --> 22:58.960
Yeah.

22:58.960 --> 23:02.964
But your point is well
taken, and I deserved that.

23:02.964 --> 23:04.466
Well, great.

23:04.466 --> 23:05.967
(chuckling)

23:05.967 --> 23:07.469
All right.

23:07.469 --> 23:08.970
Come on. Let's go.

23:08.970 --> 23:10.972
No.

23:12.474 --> 23:13.475
What do you mean "no"?

23:13.475 --> 23:14.976
Oh, all right, I see what you doing.

23:14.976 --> 23:16.478
That's good. That's, that's very funny.

23:16.478 --> 23:17.479
That's... (chuckles)

23:17.479 --> 23:19.231
All right. Come on.

23:19.231 --> 23:23.185
No, the only place I'm going is home.

23:23.185 --> 23:23.985
You know, it's very funny.

23:24.486 --> 23:25.487
