23:46.041 --> 23:48.960
When we're married,
you'll be happy we waited.

23:48.960 --> 23:50.962
Really, this is nothing
to be upset about.

23:50.962 --> 23:51.847
Bye-bye.

23:51.847 --> 23:53.298
Fine.

23:53.298 --> 23:55.300
Fine, fine, fine, fine.
I mean, it's perfect.

23:55.300 --> 23:57.803
